title: Aurosonic feat. Kate Louise Smith - Open Your Eyes (2013) (320kb

Aurosonic feat. Kate Louise Smith - Open Your Eyes (2013) 

                    Trance, Drum & Bass | How Trance Works  

            320 kbps | MP3 | single | 2013-11-25 | 00:52:42 | 121 Mb


With his signature dreamscape sound, Evgeny Smirnov, better known as Aurosonic, knows like no one else how to deliver a deep route while keeping euphoria in Trance. Supplying time after time high quality releases has earned him the well earned support from all the big trance DJs. (inc Armin van Buuren, Markus Schulz, Above and Beyond and Paul van Dyk) Together with British singer Kate Louise Smith, Aurosonic brings us the gorgeous song, Open Your Eyes. From the minute it starts, the warmth rushes in and takes over your senses. On remix duty is heavily ASOT supported Kaimo K, bringing his uplifting peak time sound! Enjoy!
